Name: Space Rocks Blaster
About the game: Become a space pilot and take the controls of different spaceships. Fly through treacherous asteroid fields and destroy the asteroids to earn points. But be careful not to crash. Aim for heart-shaped rocks to regain lost lives. Fight enemy spaceships, avoiding their powerful plasma projectiles.
